/**
 * @file  web-view-example.cpp
 * @brief Basic WebView sample: loads a URL, shows page-load events and title.
 *
 * Key bindings
 *   ESC / BACK   Quit
 *   F            GoForward
 *   B            GoBack
 *   R            Reload
